135 void CFlowOutput::SetAnalyzeSurface(const CSolver* const*solver, const CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, bool output){
136 
137  unsigned short iDim, iMarker, iMarker_Analyze;
138  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
139  su2double Mach = 0.0, Pressure, Temperature = 0.0, TotalPressure = 0.0, TotalTemperature = 0.0,
140  Enthalpy, Velocity[3] = {0.0}, TangVel[3], Vector[3], Velocity2, MassFlow, Density, Area,
141  SoundSpeed, Vn, Vn2, Vtang2, Weight = 1.0;
142 
143  const su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
144  const su2double Gamma = config->GetGamma();
145  const unsigned short nMarker = config->GetnMarker_All();
146  const unsigned short nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
147  const unsigned short Kind_Average = config->GetKind_Average();
148 
149  const bool compressible = config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE;
150  const bool incompressible = config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::INCOMPRESSIBLE;
151  const bool energy = config->GetEnergy_Equation();
152  const bool streamwisePeriodic = (config->GetKind_Streamwise_Periodic() != ENUM_STREAMWISE_PERIODIC::NONE);
153  const bool species = config->GetKind_Species_Model() != SPECIES_MODEL::NONE;
154  const auto nSpecies = config->GetnSpecies();
155 
156  const bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
157  const unsigned short nMarker_Analyze = config->GetnMarker_Analyze();
158 
159  const auto flow_nodes = solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes();
160  const CVariable* species_nodes = species ? solver[SPECIES_SOL]->GetNodes() : nullptr;
161 
162  vector<su2double> Surface_MassFlow (nMarker,0.0);
163  vector<su2double> Surface_Mach (nMarker,0.0);
164  vector<su2double> Surface_Temperature (nMarker,0.0);
165  vector<su2double> Surface_Density (nMarker,0.0);
166  vector<su2double> Surface_Enthalpy (nMarker,0.0);
167  vector<su2double> Surface_NormalVelocity (nMarker,0.0);
168  vector<su2double> Surface_StreamVelocity2 (nMarker,0.0);
169  vector<su2double> Surface_TransvVelocity2 (nMarker,0.0);
170  vector<su2double> Surface_Pressure (nMarker,0.0);
171  vector<su2double> Surface_TotalTemperature (nMarker,0.0);
172  vector<su2double> Surface_TotalPressure (nMarker,0.0);
173  vector<su2double> Surface_VelocityIdeal (nMarker,0.0);
174  vector<su2double> Surface_Area (nMarker,0.0);
175  vector<su2double> Surface_MassFlow_Abs (nMarker,0.0);
176  su2activematrix Surface_Species(nMarker, nSpecies);
177  Surface_Species = su2double(0.0);
178 
179  su2double Tot_Surface_MassFlow = 0.0;
180  su2double Tot_Surface_Mach = 0.0;
181  su2double Tot_Surface_Temperature = 0.0;
182  su2double Tot_Surface_Density = 0.0;
183  su2double Tot_Surface_Enthalpy = 0.0;
184  su2double Tot_Surface_NormalVelocity = 0.0;
185  su2double Tot_Surface_StreamVelocity2 = 0.0;
186  su2double Tot_Surface_TransvVelocity2 = 0.0;
187  su2double Tot_Surface_Pressure = 0.0;
188  su2double Tot_Surface_TotalTemperature = 0.0;
189  su2double Tot_Surface_TotalPressure = 0.0;
190  su2double Tot_Momentum_Distortion = 0.0;
191  su2double Tot_SecondOverUniformity = 0.0;
192  vector<su2double> Tot_Surface_Species(nSpecies,0.0);
193 
194  /*--- Compute the numerical fan face Mach number, and the total area of the inflow ---*/
195 
196  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
197 
198  if (config->GetMarker_All_Analyze(iMarker) == YES) {
199 
200  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
201 
202  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
203 
204  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
205 
206  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
207 
208  const su2double AxiFactor = GetAxiFactor(axisymmetric, *geometry->nodes, iPoint, iMarker);
209 
210  Density = flow_nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
211  Velocity2 = 0.0; Area = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0; Vn = 0.0; Vtang2 = 0.0;
212 
213  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
214  Area += (Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor) * (Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor);
215  Velocity[iDim] = flow_nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
216  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim] * Velocity[iDim];
217  Vn += Velocity[iDim] * Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor;
218  MassFlow += Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor * Density * Velocity[iDim];
219  }
220 
221  Area = sqrt (Area);
222  if (AxiFactor == 0.0) Vn = 0.0; else Vn /= Area;
223  Vn2 = Vn * Vn;
224  Pressure = flow_nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
225  /*--- Use recovered pressure here as pressure difference between in and outlet is zero otherwise ---*/
226  if(streamwisePeriodic) Pressure = flow_nodes->GetStreamwise_Periodic_RecoveredPressure(iPoint);
227  SoundSpeed = flow_nodes->GetSoundSpeed(iPoint);
228 
229  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
230  TangVel[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] - Vn*Vector[iDim]*AxiFactor/Area;
231  Vtang2 += TangVel[iDim]*TangVel[iDim];
232  }
233 
234  if (incompressible){
235  if (config->GetKind_DensityModel() == INC_DENSITYMODEL::VARIABLE) {
236  Mach = sqrt(flow_nodes->GetVelocity2(iPoint))/
237  sqrt(flow_nodes->GetSpecificHeatCp(iPoint)*config->GetPressure_ThermodynamicND()/(flow_nodes->GetSpecificHeatCv(iPoint)*flow_nodes->GetDensity(iPoint)));
238  } else {
239  Mach = sqrt(flow_nodes->GetVelocity2(iPoint))/
240  sqrt(config->GetBulk_Modulus()/(flow_nodes->GetDensity(iPoint)));
241  }
242  Temperature = flow_nodes->GetTemperature(iPoint);
243  Enthalpy = flow_nodes->GetSpecificHeatCp(iPoint)*Temperature;
244  TotalTemperature = Temperature + 0.5*Velocity2/flow_nodes->GetSpecificHeatCp(iPoint);
245  TotalPressure = Pressure + 0.5*Density*Velocity2;
246  }
247  else{
248  Mach = sqrt(Velocity2)/SoundSpeed;
249  Temperature = Pressure / (Gas_Constant * Density);
250  Enthalpy = flow_nodes->GetEnthalpy(iPoint);
251  TotalTemperature = Temperature * (1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
252  TotalPressure = Pressure * pow( 1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
253  }
254 
255  /*--- Compute the mass Surface_MassFlow ---*/
256 
257  Surface_Area[iMarker] += Area;
258  Surface_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
259  Surface_MassFlow_Abs[iMarker] += abs(MassFlow);
260 
261  if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_MASSFLUX) Weight = abs(MassFlow);
262  else if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_AREA) Weight = abs(Area);
263  else Weight = 1.0;
264 
265  Surface_Mach[iMarker] += Mach*Weight;
266  Surface_Temperature[iMarker] += Temperature*Weight;
267  Surface_Density[iMarker] += Density*Weight;
268  Surface_Enthalpy[iMarker] += Enthalpy*Weight;
269  Surface_NormalVelocity[iMarker] += Vn*Weight;
270  Surface_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*Weight;
271  Surface_TotalTemperature[iMarker] += TotalTemperature*Weight;
272  Surface_TotalPressure[iMarker] += TotalPressure*Weight;
273  if (species)
274  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nSpecies; iVar++)
275  Surface_Species(iMarker, iVar) += species_nodes->GetSolution(iPoint, iVar)*Weight;
276 
277  /*--- For now, always used the area to weight the uniformities. ---*/
278 
279  Weight = abs(Area);
280 
281  Surface_StreamVelocity2[iMarker] += Vn2*Weight;
282  Surface_TransvVelocity2[iMarker] += Vtang2*Weight;
283 
284  }
285  }
286  }
287  }
288 
289  /*--- Copy to the appropriate structure ---*/
290 
291  vector<su2double> Surface_MassFlow_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
292  vector<su2double> Surface_Mach_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
293  vector<su2double> Surface_Temperature_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
294  vector<su2double> Surface_Density_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
295  vector<su2double> Surface_Enthalpy_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
296  vector<su2double> Surface_NormalVelocity_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
297  vector<su2double> Surface_StreamVelocity2_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
298  vector<su2double> Surface_TransvVelocity2_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
299  vector<su2double> Surface_Pressure_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
300  vector<su2double> Surface_TotalTemperature_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
301  vector<su2double> Surface_TotalPressure_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
302  vector<su2double> Surface_Area_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
303  vector<su2double> Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Local (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
304  su2activematrix Surface_Species_Local(nMarker_Analyze,nSpecies);
305  Surface_Species_Local = su2double(0.0);
306 
307  vector<su2double> Surface_MassFlow_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
308  vector<su2double> Surface_Mach_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
309  vector<su2double> Surface_Temperature_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
310  vector<su2double> Surface_Density_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
311  vector<su2double> Surface_Enthalpy_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
312  vector<su2double> Surface_NormalVelocity_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
313  vector<su2double> Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
314  vector<su2double> Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
315  vector<su2double> Surface_Pressure_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
316  vector<su2double> Surface_TotalTemperature_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
317  vector<su2double> Surface_TotalPressure_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
318  vector<su2double> Surface_Area_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
319  vector<su2double> Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
320  su2activematrix Surface_Species_Total(nMarker_Analyze,nSpecies);
321  Surface_Species_Total = su2double(0.0);
322 
323  vector<su2double> Surface_MomentumDistortion_Total (nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
324 
325  /*--- Compute the numerical fan face Mach number, mach number, temperature and the total area ---*/
326 
327  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
328 
329  if (config->GetMarker_All_Analyze(iMarker) == YES) {
330 
331  for (iMarker_Analyze= 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
332 
333  /*--- Add the Surface_MassFlow, and Surface_Area to the particular boundary ---*/
334 
335  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == config->GetMarker_Analyze_TagBound(iMarker_Analyze)) {
336  Surface_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_MassFlow[iMarker];
337  Surface_Mach_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Mach[iMarker];
338  Surface_Temperature_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Temperature[iMarker];
339  Surface_Density_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Density[iMarker];
340  Surface_Enthalpy_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Enthalpy[iMarker];
341  Surface_NormalVelocity_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_NormalVelocity[iMarker];
342  Surface_StreamVelocity2_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_StreamVelocity2[iMarker];
343  Surface_TransvVelocity2_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_TransvVelocity2[iMarker];
344  Surface_Pressure_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Pressure[iMarker];
345  Surface_TotalTemperature_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_TotalTemperature[iMarker];
346  Surface_TotalPressure_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_TotalPressure[iMarker];
347  Surface_Area_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Area[iMarker];
348  Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_MassFlow_Abs[iMarker];
349  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nSpecies; iVar++)
350  Surface_Species_Local(iMarker_Analyze, iVar) += Surface_Species(iMarker, iVar);
351  }
352 
353  }
354 
355  }
356 
357  }

359  auto Allreduce = [](const vector<su2double>& src, vector<su2double>& dst) {
360  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(src.data(), dst.data(), src.size(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
361  };
362 
363  auto Allreduce_su2activematrix = [](const su2activematrix& src, su2activematrix& dst) {
364  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(src.data(), dst.data(), src.size(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
365  };
366 
367  Allreduce(Surface_MassFlow_Local, Surface_MassFlow_Total);
368  Allreduce(Surface_Mach_Local, Surface_Mach_Total);
369  Allreduce(Surface_Temperature_Local, Surface_Temperature_Total);
370  Allreduce(Surface_Density_Local, Surface_Density_Total);
371  Allreduce(Surface_Enthalpy_Local, Surface_Enthalpy_Total);
372  Allreduce(Surface_NormalVelocity_Local, Surface_NormalVelocity_Total);
373  Allreduce(Surface_StreamVelocity2_Local, Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total);
374  Allreduce(Surface_TransvVelocity2_Local, Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total);
375  Allreduce(Surface_Pressure_Local, Surface_Pressure_Total);
376  Allreduce(Surface_TotalTemperature_Local, Surface_TotalTemperature_Total);
377  Allreduce(Surface_TotalPressure_Local, Surface_TotalPressure_Total);
378  Allreduce(Surface_Area_Local, Surface_Area_Total);
379  Allreduce(Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Local, Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total);
380  Allreduce_su2activematrix(Surface_Species_Local, Surface_Species_Total);
381 
382 
383  /*--- Compute the value of Surface_Area_Total, and Surface_Pressure_Total, and
384  set the value in the config structure for future use ---*/
385 
386  for (iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
387 
388  if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_MASSFLUX) Weight = Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total[iMarker_Analyze];
389  else if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_AREA) Weight = abs(Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze]);
390  else Weight = 1.0;
391 
392  if (Weight != 0.0) {
393  Surface_Mach_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
394  Surface_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
395  Surface_Density_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
396  Surface_Enthalpy_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
397  Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
398  Surface_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
399  Surface_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
400  Surface_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
401  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nSpecies; iVar++)
402  Surface_Species_Total(iMarker_Analyze, iVar) /= Weight;
403  }
404  else {
405  Surface_Mach_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
406  Surface_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
407  Surface_Density_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
408  Surface_Enthalpy_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
409  Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
410  Surface_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
411  Surface_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
412  Surface_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
413  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nSpecies; iVar++)
414  Surface_Species_Total(iMarker_Analyze, iVar) = 0.0;
415  }
416 
417  /*--- Compute flow uniformity parameters separately (always area for now). ---*/
418 
419  Area = fabs(Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze]);
420 
421  /*--- The definitions for Distortion and Uniformity Parameters are taken as defined by Banko, Andrew J., et al. in section 3.2 of
422  https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0142727X16301412 ------*/
423 
424  if (Area != 0.0) {
425  Surface_MomentumDistortion_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze]/(Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze]*Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze]*Area) - 1.0;
426  Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Area;
427  Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Area;
428  }
429  else {
430  Surface_MomentumDistortion_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
431  Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
432  Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
433  }
434 
435  }
436 
437  for (iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
438 
439  su2double MassFlow = Surface_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
440  if (us_units) MassFlow *= 32.174;
441  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_MASSFLOW", MassFlow, iMarker_Analyze);
442  Tot_Surface_MassFlow += MassFlow;
443  config->SetSurface_MassFlow(iMarker_Analyze, MassFlow);
444 
445  su2double Mach = Surface_Mach_Total[iMarker_Analyze];
446  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_MACH", Mach, iMarker_Analyze);
447  Tot_Surface_Mach += Mach;
448  config->SetSurface_Mach(iMarker_Analyze, Mach);
449 
450  su2double Temperature = Surface_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetTemperature_Ref();
451  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_STATIC_TEMPERATURE", Temperature, iMarker_Analyze);
452  Tot_Surface_Temperature += Temperature;
453  config->SetSurface_Temperature(iMarker_Analyze, Temperature);
454 
455  su2double Pressure = Surface_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetPressure_Ref();
456  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_STATIC_PRESSURE", Pressure, iMarker_Analyze);
457  Tot_Surface_Pressure += Pressure;
458  config->SetSurface_Pressure(iMarker_Analyze, Pressure);
459 
460  su2double Density = Surface_Density_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetDensity_Ref();
461  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("AVG_DENSITY", Density, iMarker_Analyze);
462  Tot_Surface_Density += Density;
463  config->SetSurface_Density(iMarker_Analyze, Density);
464 
465  su2double Enthalpy = Surface_Enthalpy_Total[iMarker_Analyze];
466  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("AVG_ENTHALPY", Enthalpy, iMarker_Analyze);
467  Tot_Surface_Enthalpy += Enthalpy;
468  config->SetSurface_Enthalpy(iMarker_Analyze, Enthalpy);
469 
470  su2double NormalVelocity = Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
471  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("AVG_NORMALVEL", NormalVelocity, iMarker_Analyze);
472  Tot_Surface_NormalVelocity += NormalVelocity;
473  config->SetSurface_NormalVelocity(iMarker_Analyze, NormalVelocity);
474 
475  su2double Uniformity = sqrt(Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze]) * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
476  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_UNIFORMITY", Uniformity, iMarker_Analyze);
477  Tot_Surface_StreamVelocity2 += Uniformity;
478  config->SetSurface_Uniformity(iMarker_Analyze, Uniformity);
479 
480  su2double SecondaryStrength = sqrt(Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze]) * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
481  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_SECONDARY", SecondaryStrength, iMarker_Analyze);
482  Tot_Surface_TransvVelocity2 += SecondaryStrength;
483  config->SetSurface_SecondaryStrength(iMarker_Analyze, SecondaryStrength);
484 
485  su2double MomentumDistortion = Surface_MomentumDistortion_Total[iMarker_Analyze];
486  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_MOM_DISTORTION", MomentumDistortion, iMarker_Analyze);
487  Tot_Momentum_Distortion += MomentumDistortion;
488  config->SetSurface_MomentumDistortion(iMarker_Analyze, MomentumDistortion);
489 
490  su2double SecondOverUniform = SecondaryStrength/Uniformity;
491  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_SECOND_OVER_UNIFORM", SecondOverUniform, iMarker_Analyze);
492  Tot_SecondOverUniformity += SecondOverUniform;
493  config->SetSurface_SecondOverUniform(iMarker_Analyze, SecondOverUniform);
494 
495  su2double TotalTemperature = Surface_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetTemperature_Ref();
496  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_TOTAL_TEMPERATURE", TotalTemperature, iMarker_Analyze);
497  Tot_Surface_TotalTemperature += TotalTemperature;
498  config->SetSurface_TotalTemperature(iMarker_Analyze, TotalTemperature);
499 
500  su2double TotalPressure = Surface_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetPressure_Ref();
501  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_TOTAL_PRESSURE", TotalPressure, iMarker_Analyze);
502  Tot_Surface_TotalPressure += TotalPressure;
503  config->SetSurface_TotalPressure(iMarker_Analyze, TotalPressure);
504 
505  if (species) {
506  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nSpecies; iVar++) {
507  su2double Species = Surface_Species_Total(iMarker_Analyze, iVar);
508  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_SPECIES_" + std::to_string(iVar), Species, iMarker_Analyze);
509  Tot_Surface_Species[iVar] += Species;
510  if (iVar == 0)
511  config->SetSurface_Species_0(iMarker_Analyze, Species);
512  }
513  }
514  }
515 
516  /*--- Compute the average static pressure drop between two surfaces. Note
517  that this assumes we have two surfaces being analyzed and that the outlet
518  is first followed by the inlet. This is because we may also want to choose
519  outlet values (temperature, uniformity, etc.) for our design problems,
520  which require the outlet to be listed first. This is a simple first version
521  that could be generalized to a different orders/lists/etc. ---*/
522 
523  if (nMarker_Analyze >= 2) {
524  su2double PressureDrop = (Surface_Pressure_Total[1] - Surface_Pressure_Total[0]) * config->GetPressure_Ref();
525  for (iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
526  config->SetSurface_PressureDrop(iMarker_Analyze, PressureDrop);
527  }
528  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_PRESSURE_DROP", PressureDrop);
529  }
530  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_MASSFLOW", Tot_Surface_MassFlow);
531  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_MACH", Tot_Surface_Mach);
532  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_STATIC_TEMPERATURE", Tot_Surface_Temperature);
533  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_STATIC_PRESSURE", Tot_Surface_Pressure);
534  SetHistoryOutputValue("AVG_DENSITY", Tot_Surface_Density);
535  SetHistoryOutputValue("AVG_ENTHALPY", Tot_Surface_Enthalpy);
536  SetHistoryOutputValue("AVG_NORMALVEL", Tot_Surface_NormalVelocity);
537  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_UNIFORMITY", Tot_Surface_StreamVelocity2);
538  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_SECONDARY", Tot_Surface_TransvVelocity2);
539  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_MOM_DISTORTION", Tot_Momentum_Distortion);
540  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_SECOND_OVER_UNIFORM", Tot_SecondOverUniformity);
541  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_TOTAL_TEMPERATURE", Tot_Surface_TotalTemperature);
542  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_TOTAL_PRESSURE", Tot_Surface_TotalPressure);
543  if (species) {
544  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nSpecies; iVar++)
545  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_SPECIES_" + std::to_string(iVar), Tot_Surface_Species[iVar]);
546 
547  SetAnalyzeSurface_SpeciesVariance(solver, geometry, config, Surface_Species_Total, Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total,
548  Surface_Area_Total);
549  }
550 
551  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && !config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint() && output) {
552 
553  cout.precision(6);
554  cout.setf(ios::scientific, ios::floatfield);
555  cout << endl << "Computing surface mean values." << endl << endl;
556 
557  for (iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
558  cout << "Surface "<< config->GetMarker_Analyze_TagBound(iMarker_Analyze) << ":" << endl;
559 
560  if (nDim == 3) { if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "Area (m^2): "; else cout << setw(20) << "Area (ft^2): "; }
561  else { if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "Area (m): "; else cout << setw(20) << "Area (ft): "; }
562 
563  if (si_units) cout << setw(15) << fabs(Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze]);
564  else if (us_units) cout << setw(15) << fabs(Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze])*12.0*12.0;
565 
566  cout << endl;
567 
568  su2double MassFlow = config->GetSurface_MassFlow(iMarker_Analyze);
569  if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "Mf (kg/s): " << setw(15) << MassFlow;
570  else if (us_units) cout << setw(20) << "Mf (lbs/s): " << setw(15) << MassFlow;
571 
572  su2double NormalVelocity = config->GetSurface_NormalVelocity(iMarker_Analyze);
573  if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "Vn (m/s): " << setw(15) << NormalVelocity;
574  else if (us_units) cout << setw(20) << "Vn (ft/s): " << setw(15) << NormalVelocity;
575 
576  cout << endl;
577 
578  su2double Uniformity = config->GetSurface_Uniformity(iMarker_Analyze);
579  if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "Uniformity (m/s): " << setw(15) << Uniformity;
580  else if (us_units) cout << setw(20) << "Uniformity (ft/s): " << setw(15) << Uniformity;
581 
582  su2double SecondaryStrength = config->GetSurface_SecondaryStrength(iMarker_Analyze);
583  if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "Secondary (m/s): " << setw(15) << SecondaryStrength;
584  else if (us_units) cout << setw(20) << "Secondary (ft/s): " << setw(15) << SecondaryStrength;
585 
586  cout << endl;
587 
588  su2double MomentumDistortion = config->GetSurface_MomentumDistortion(iMarker_Analyze);
589  cout << setw(20) << "Mom. Distortion: " << setw(15) << MomentumDistortion;
590 
591  su2double SecondOverUniform = config->GetSurface_SecondOverUniform(iMarker_Analyze);
592  cout << setw(20) << "Second/Uniform: " << setw(15) << SecondOverUniform;
593 
594  cout << endl;
595 
596  su2double Pressure = config->GetSurface_Pressure(iMarker_Analyze);
597  if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "P (Pa): " << setw(15) << Pressure;
598  else if (us_units) cout << setw(20) << "P (psf): " << setw(15) << Pressure;
599 
600  su2double TotalPressure = config->GetSurface_TotalPressure(iMarker_Analyze);
601  if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "PT (Pa): " << setw(15) <<TotalPressure;
602  else if (us_units) cout << setw(20) << "PT (psf): " << setw(15) <<TotalPressure;
603 
604  cout << endl;
605 
606  su2double Mach = config->GetSurface_Mach(iMarker_Analyze);
607  cout << setw(20) << "Mach: " << setw(15) << Mach;
608 
609  su2double Density = config->GetSurface_Density(iMarker_Analyze);
610  if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "Rho (kg/m^3): " << setw(15) << Density;
611  else if (us_units) cout << setw(20) << "Rho (lb/ft^3): " << setw(15) << Density*32.174;
612 
613  cout << endl;
614 
615  if (compressible || energy) {
616  su2double Temperature = config->GetSurface_Temperature(iMarker_Analyze);
617  if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "T (K): " << setw(15) << Temperature;
618  else if (us_units) cout << setw(20) << "T (R): " << setw(15) << Temperature;
619 
620  su2double TotalTemperature = config->GetSurface_TotalTemperature(iMarker_Analyze);
621  if (si_units) cout << setw(20) << "TT (K): " << setw(15) << TotalTemperature;
622  else if (us_units) cout << setw(20) << "TT (R): " << setw(15) << TotalTemperature;
623 
624  cout << endl;
625  }
626 
627  }
628  cout.unsetf(ios_base::floatfield);
629 
630  }
631 
632  std::cout << std::resetiosflags(std::cout.flags());
633 }

635 void CFlowOutput::SetAnalyzeSurface_SpeciesVariance(const CSolver* const*solver, const CGeometry *geometry,
636  CConfig *config, const su2activematrix& Surface_Species_Total,
637  const vector<su2double>& Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total,
638  const vector<su2double>& Surface_Area_Total) {
639 
640  const unsigned short nMarker = config->GetnMarker_All();
641  const unsigned short Kind_Average = config->GetKind_Average();
642 
643  const bool species = config->GetKind_Species_Model() != SPECIES_MODEL::NONE;
644  const auto nSpecies = config->GetnSpecies();
645 
646  const bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
647  const unsigned short nMarker_Analyze = config->GetnMarker_Analyze();
648 
649  const auto flow_nodes = solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes();
650  const CVariable* species_nodes = species ? solver[SPECIES_SOL]->GetNodes() : nullptr;
651 
652  /*--- Compute Variance of species on the analyze markers. This is done after the rest as the average species value is
653  * necessary. The variance is computed for all species together and not for each species alone. ---*/
654  vector<su2double> Surface_SpeciesVariance(nMarker,0.0);
655  su2double Tot_Surface_SpeciesVariance = 0.0;
656 
657  /*--- sum += (Yj_i - mu_Yj)^2 * weight_i with i representing the node and j the species. ---*/
658  for (unsigned short iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
659 
660  if (config->GetMarker_All_Analyze(iMarker) == YES) {
661 
662  /*--- Find iMarkerAnalyze to iMarker. As SpeciesAvg is accessed via iMarkerAnalyze. ---*/
663  unsigned short iMarker_Analyze_Stored = std::numeric_limits<unsigned short>::max();
664  for (unsigned short iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++)
665  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == config->GetMarker_Analyze_TagBound(iMarker_Analyze))
666  iMarker_Analyze_Stored = iMarker_Analyze;
667 
668  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
669  const auto iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
670 
671  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
672 
673  const su2double AxiFactor = GetAxiFactor(axisymmetric, *geometry->nodes, iPoint, iMarker);
674 
675  su2double Vector[3];
676  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
677  const su2double Density = flow_nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
678  su2double Area = 0.0;
679  su2double MassFlow = 0.0;
680 
681  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
682  Area += (Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor) * (Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor);
683  MassFlow += Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor * Density * flow_nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
684  }
685  Area= sqrt(Area);
686 
687  su2double Weight;
688  if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_MASSFLUX) Weight = abs(MassFlow);
689  else if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_AREA) Weight = abs(Area);
690  else Weight = 1.0;
691 
692  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nSpecies; iVar++)
693  Surface_SpeciesVariance[iMarker] += pow(species_nodes->GetSolution(iPoint, iVar) - Surface_Species_Total(iMarker_Analyze_Stored, iVar), 2) * Weight;
694  }
695  }
696  }
697  }
698 
699  /*--- MPI Communication ---*/
700  vector<su2double> Surface_SpeciesVariance_Local(nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
701  vector<su2double> Surface_SpeciesVariance_Total(nMarker_Analyze,0.0);
702 
703  for (unsigned short iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
704 
705  if (config->GetMarker_All_Analyze(iMarker) == YES) {
706 
707  for (unsigned short iMarker_Analyze= 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
708 
709  /*--- Add the Surface_MassFlow, and Surface_Area to the particular boundary ---*/
710 
711  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == config->GetMarker_Analyze_TagBound(iMarker_Analyze)) {
712  Surface_SpeciesVariance_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_SpeciesVariance[iMarker];
713  }
714  }
715  }
716  }
717 
718  auto Allreduce = [](const vector<su2double>& src, vector<su2double>& dst) {
719  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(src.data(), dst.data(), src.size(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
720  };
721  Allreduce(Surface_SpeciesVariance_Local, Surface_SpeciesVariance_Total);
722 
723  /*--- Divide quantity by weight. ---*/
724  for (unsigned short iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
725 
726  su2double Weight;
727  if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_MASSFLUX) Weight = Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total[iMarker_Analyze];
728  else if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_AREA) Weight = abs(Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze]);
729  else Weight = 1.0;
730 
731  if (Weight != 0.0) {
732  Surface_SpeciesVariance_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
733  }
734  else {
735  Surface_SpeciesVariance[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
736  }
737  }
738 
739  /*--- Set values on markers ---*/
740  for (unsigned short iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
741  su2double SpeciesVariance = Surface_SpeciesVariance_Total[iMarker_Analyze];
742  SetHistoryOutputPerSurfaceValue("SURFACE_SPECIES_VARIANCE", SpeciesVariance, iMarker_Analyze);
743  Tot_Surface_SpeciesVariance += SpeciesVariance;
744  config->SetSurface_Species_Variance(iMarker_Analyze, Tot_Surface_SpeciesVariance);
745  }
746  SetHistoryOutputValue("SURFACE_SPECIES_VARIANCE", Tot_Surface_SpeciesVariance);
747 }
748 
749 void CFlowOutput::SetCustomOutputs(const CSolver* const* solver, const CGeometry *geometry, const CConfig *config) {
750 
751  const bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
752  const auto* flowNodes = su2staticcast_p<const CFlowVariable*>(solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes());
753 
754  for (auto& output : customOutputs) {
755  if (output.varIndices.empty()) {
756  /*--- Setup indices for the symbols in the expression. ---*/
757 
758  if (config->GetNEMOProblem()) {
759  ConvertVariableSymbolsToIndices(
760  CNEMOEulerVariable::template CIndices<unsigned long>(nDim, config->GetnSpecies()), output);
761  } else if (config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE) {
762  ConvertVariableSymbolsToIndices(CEulerVariable::template CIndices<unsigned long>(nDim, 0), output);
763  } else if (config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::INCOMPRESSIBLE) {
764  ConvertVariableSymbolsToIndices(CIncEulerVariable::template CIndices<unsigned long>(nDim, 0), output);
765  } else {
766  SU2_MPI::Error("Unknown flow solver type.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
767  }
768  /*--- Convert marker names to their index (if any) in this rank. ---*/
769 
770  output.markerIndices.clear();
771  for (const auto& marker : output.markers) {
772  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); ++iMarker) {
773  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == marker) {
774  output.markerIndices.push_back(iMarker);
775  continue;
776  }
777  }
778  }
779  }
780 
781  if (output.type == OperationType::FUNCTION) {
782  auto Functor = [&](unsigned long i) {
783  /*--- Functions only reference other history outputs. ---*/
784  return *output.otherOutputs[i - CustomOutput::NOT_A_VARIABLE];
785  };
786  SetHistoryOutputValue(output.name, output.eval(Functor));
787  continue;
788  }
789 
790  /*--- Surface integral of the expression. ---*/
791 
792  std::array<su2double, 2> integral = {0.0, 0.0};
793 
794  SU2_OMP_PARALLEL {
795  std::array<su2double, 2> local_integral = {0.0, 0.0};
796 
797  for (const auto iMarker : output.markerIndices) {
798 
799  SU2_OMP_FOR_(schedule(static) SU2_NOWAIT)
800  for (auto iVertex = 0ul; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; ++iVertex) {
801  const auto iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
802 
803  if (!geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) continue;
804 
805  const auto* normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
806 
807  su2double weight = 1.0;
808  if (output.type == OperationType::MASSFLOW_AVG || output.type == OperationType::MASSFLOW_INT) {
809  weight = flowNodes->GetDensity(iPoint) * flowNodes->GetProjVel(iPoint, normal);
810  } else {
811  weight = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, normal);
812  }
813  weight *= GetAxiFactor(axisymmetric, *geometry->nodes, iPoint, iMarker);
814  local_integral[1] += weight;
815 
816  /*--- Prepare the functor that maps symbol indices to values (see ConvertVariableSymbolsToIndices). ---*/
817 
818  auto Functor = [&](unsigned long i) {
819  if (i < CustomOutput::NOT_A_VARIABLE) {
820  const auto solIdx = i / CustomOutput::MAX_VARS_PER_SOLVER;
821  const auto varIdx = i % CustomOutput::MAX_VARS_PER_SOLVER;
822  if (solIdx == FLOW_SOL) {
823  return flowNodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint, varIdx);
824  } else {
825  return solver[solIdx]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint, varIdx);
826  }
827  } else {
828  return *output.otherOutputs[i - CustomOutput::NOT_A_VARIABLE];
829  }
830  };
831  local_integral[0] += weight * output.eval(Functor);
832  }
833  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
834  }
835 
836  SU2_OMP_CRITICAL {
837  integral[0] += local_integral[0];
838  integral[1] += local_integral[1];
839  }
840  END_SU2_OMP_CRITICAL
841  }
842  END_SU2_OMP_PARALLEL
843 
844  const auto local = integral;
845  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(local.data(), integral.data(), 2, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
846  if (output.type == OperationType::AREA_AVG || output.type == OperationType::MASSFLOW_AVG) {
847  integral[0] /= integral[1];
848  }
849  SetHistoryOutputValue(output.name, integral[0]);
850  }
851 }
852

1158 void CFlowOutput::LoadVolumeData_Scalar(const CConfig* config, const CSolver* const* solver, const CGeometry* geometry,
1159  const unsigned long iPoint) {
1160  const auto* turb_solver = solver[TURB_SOL];
1161  const auto* trans_solver = solver[TRANS_SOL];
1162  const auto* Node_Flow = solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes();
1163  const auto* Node_Turb = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE) ? turb_solver->GetNodes() : nullptr;
1164  const auto* Node_Trans = (config->GetKind_Trans_Model() != TURB_TRANS_MODEL::NONE) ? trans_solver->GetNodes() : nullptr;
1165  const auto* Node_Geo = geometry->nodes;
1166 
1167  if (config->GetViscous()) {
1168  if (nDim == 3){
1169  SetVolumeOutputValue("VORTICITY_X", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVorticity(iPoint)[0]);
1170  SetVolumeOutputValue("VORTICITY_Y", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVorticity(iPoint)[1]);
1171  SetVolumeOutputValue("VORTICITY_Z", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVorticity(iPoint)[2]);
1172  } else {
1173  SetVolumeOutputValue("VORTICITY", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVorticity(iPoint)[2]);
1174  }
1175  SetVolumeOutputValue("Q_CRITERION", iPoint, GetQ_Criterion(Node_Flow->GetVelocityGradient(iPoint)));
1176  }
1177 
1178  const bool limiter = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Turb() != LIMITER::NONE);
1179 
1180  switch (TurbModelFamily(config->GetKind_Turb_Model())) {
1181  case TURB_FAMILY::SA:
1182  SetVolumeOutputValue("NU_TILDE", iPoint, Node_Turb->GetSolution(iPoint, 0));
1183  SetVolumeOutputValue("RES_NU_TILDE", iPoint, turb_solver->LinSysRes(iPoint, 0));
1184  if (limiter) {
1185  SetVolumeOutputValue("LIMITER_NU_TILDE", iPoint, Node_Turb->GetLimiter(iPoint, 0));
1186  }
1187  break;
1188 
1189  case TURB_FAMILY::KW:
1190  SetVolumeOutputValue("TKE", iPoint, Node_Turb->GetSolution(iPoint, 0));
1191  SetVolumeOutputValue("DISSIPATION", iPoint, Node_Turb->GetSolution(iPoint, 1));
1192  SetVolumeOutputValue("RES_TKE", iPoint, turb_solver->LinSysRes(iPoint, 0));
1193  SetVolumeOutputValue("RES_DISSIPATION", iPoint, turb_solver->LinSysRes(iPoint, 1));
1194  if (limiter) {
1195  SetVolumeOutputValue("LIMITER_TKE", iPoint, Node_Turb->GetLimiter(iPoint, 0));
1196  SetVolumeOutputValue("LIMITER_DISSIPATION", iPoint, Node_Turb->GetLimiter(iPoint, 1));
1197  }
1198  break;
1199 
1200  case TURB_FAMILY::NONE: break;
1201  }
1202 
1203  /*--- If we got here a turbulence model is being used, therefore there is eddy viscosity. ---*/
1204  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE) {
1205  SetVolumeOutputValue("EDDY_VISCOSITY", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint));
1206  }
1207 
1208  if (config->GetSAParsedOptions().bc) {
1209  SetVolumeOutputValue("INTERMITTENCY", iPoint, Node_Turb->GetIntermittencyEff(iPoint));
1210  }
1211 
1212  switch (config->GetKind_Trans_Model()) {
1213  case TURB_TRANS_MODEL::LM:
1214  SetVolumeOutputValue("INTERMITTENCY", iPoint, Node_Trans->GetSolution(iPoint, 0));
1215  SetVolumeOutputValue("RE_THETA_T", iPoint, Node_Trans->GetSolution(iPoint, 1));
1216  SetVolumeOutputValue("INTERMITTENCY_SEP", iPoint, Node_Trans->GetIntermittencySep(iPoint));
1217  SetVolumeOutputValue("INTERMITTENCY_EFF", iPoint, Node_Trans->GetIntermittencyEff(iPoint));
1218  SetVolumeOutputValue("TURB_INDEX", iPoint, Node_Turb->GetTurbIndex(iPoint));
1219  SetVolumeOutputValue("RES_INTERMITTENCY", iPoint, trans_solver->LinSysRes(iPoint, 0));
1220  SetVolumeOutputValue("RES_RE_THETA_T", iPoint, trans_solver->LinSysRes(iPoint, 1));
1221  break;
1222 
1223  case TURB_TRANS_MODEL::NONE: break;
1224  }
1225 
1226  if (config->GetKind_HybridRANSLES() != NO_HYBRIDRANSLES) {
1227  SetVolumeOutputValue("DES_LENGTHSCALE", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetDES_LengthScale(iPoint));
1228  SetVolumeOutputValue("WALL_DISTANCE", iPoint, Node_Geo->GetWall_Distance(iPoint));
1229  }
1230 
1231  if (config->GetKind_Species_Model() != SPECIES_MODEL::NONE) {
1232  const auto Node_Species = solver[SPECIES_SOL]->GetNodes();
1233 
1234  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < config->GetnSpecies(); iVar++) {
1235  SetVolumeOutputValue("SPECIES_" + std::to_string(iVar), iPoint, Node_Species->GetSolution(iPoint, iVar));
1236  SetVolumeOutputValue("RES_SPECIES_" + std::to_string(iVar), iPoint, solver[SPECIES_SOL]->LinSysRes(iPoint, iVar));
1237  if (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Species() != LIMITER::NONE)
1238  SetVolumeOutputValue("LIMITER_SPECIES_" + std::to_string(iVar), iPoint, Node_Species->GetLimiter(iPoint, iVar));
1239  }
1240  }
1241 }

1243 void CFlowOutput::LoadSurfaceData(CConfig *config, CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver, unsigned long iPoint, unsigned short iMarker, unsigned long iVertex){
1244 
1245  if (!config->GetViscous_Wall(iMarker)) return;
1246 
1247  const auto heat_sol = (config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::INCOMPRESSIBLE) &&
1248  config->GetWeakly_Coupled_Heat() ? HEAT_SOL : FLOW_SOL;
1249 
1250  SetVolumeOutputValue("SKIN_FRICTION-X", iPoint, solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetCSkinFriction(iMarker, iVertex, 0));

1415 void CFlowOutput::Set_CpInverseDesign(CSolver *solver, const CGeometry *geometry, const CConfig *config){
1416 
1417  /*--- Prepare to read the surface pressure files (CSV) ---*/
1418 
1419  const auto surfCp_filename = config->GetUnsteady_FileName("TargetCp", curTimeIter, ".dat");
1420 
1421  /*--- Read the surface pressure file, on the first inner iteration. ---*/
1422 
1423  ifstream Surface_file;
1424  Surface_file.open(surfCp_filename);
1425 
1426  if (!Surface_file.good()) {
1427  solver->SetTotal_CpDiff(0.0);
1428  SetHistoryOutputValue("INVERSE_DESIGN_PRESSURE", 0.0);
1429  return;
1430  }
1431 
1432  if ((config->GetInnerIter() == 0) || config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()) {
1433  string text_line;
1434  getline(Surface_file, text_line);
1435 
1436  while (getline(Surface_file, text_line)) {
1437  /*--- remove commas ---*/
1438  for (auto& c : text_line) if (c == ',') c = ' ';
1439  stringstream point_line(text_line);
1440 
1441  /*--- parse line ---*/
1442  unsigned long iPointGlobal;
1443  su2double XCoord, YCoord, ZCoord=0, Pressure, PressureCoeff;
1444 
1445  point_line >> iPointGlobal >> XCoord >> YCoord;
1446  if (nDim == 3) point_line >> ZCoord;
1447  point_line >> Pressure >> PressureCoeff;
1448 
1449  const auto iPoint = geometry->GetGlobal_to_Local_Point(iPointGlobal);
1450 
1451  /*--- If the point is on this rank set the Cp to associated vertices
1452  * (one point may be shared by multiple vertices). ---*/
1453  if (iPoint >= 0) {
1454  bool set = false;
1455  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < geometry->GetnMarker(); ++iMarker) {
1456  const auto iVertex = geometry->nodes->GetVertex(iPoint, iMarker);
1457 
1458  if (iVertex >= 0) {
1459  solver->SetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex, PressureCoeff);
1460  set = true;
1461  }
1462  }
1463  if (!set)
1464  cout << "WARNING: In file " << surfCp_filename << ", point " << iPointGlobal << " is not a vertex." << endl;
1465  }
1466  }
1467  }
1468 
1469  /*--- Compute the pressure difference. ---*/
1470 
1471  su2double PressDiff = 0.0;
1472 
1473  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < geometry->GetnMarker(); ++iMarker) {
1474 
1475  const auto Boundary = config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker);
1476 
1477  if (config->GetSolid_Wall(iMarker) || (Boundary == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)) {
1478  for (auto iVertex = 0ul; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
1479 
1480  const auto iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1481  if (!geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) continue;
1482 
1483  const auto Cp = solver->GetCPressure(iMarker, iVertex);
1484  const auto CpTarget = solver->GetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex);
1485 
1486  const auto Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
1487  const auto Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
1488 
1489  PressDiff += Area * pow(CpTarget-Cp, 2);
1490  }
1491  }
1492  }
1493  su2double tmp = PressDiff;
1494  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&tmp, &PressDiff, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1495 
1496  /*--- Update the total Cp difference coeffient. ---*/
1497 
1498  solver->SetTotal_CpDiff(PressDiff);
1499  SetHistoryOutputValue("INVERSE_DESIGN_PRESSURE", PressDiff);
1500 
1501 }

1630  vector<unsigned long> IdPoint(nVertex_NearField);
1631  vector<unsigned long> IdDomain(nVertex_NearField);
1632  vector<su2double> Pressure(nVertex_NearField);
1633  vector<su2double> FaceArea(nVertex_NearField);
1634  vector<su2double> EquivArea(nVertex_NearField);
1635  vector<su2double> TargetArea(nVertex_NearField);
1636  vector<su2double> NearFieldWeight(nVertex_NearField);
1637  vector<su2double> Weight(nVertex_NearField);
1638 
1639  nVertex_NearField = 0;
1640  for (int iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < size; iProcessor++) {
1641  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < Buffer_Receive_nVertex[iProcessor]; iVertex++) {
1642  Xcoord[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Xcoord[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
1643  Ycoord[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Ycoord[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
1644 
1645  if (nDim == 2) {
1646  AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = 0;
1647  }
1648 
1649  if (nDim == 3) {
1650  Zcoord[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Zcoord[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
1651 
1652  /*--- Rotate the nearfield cylinder ---*/
1653 
1654  su2double YcoordRot = Ycoord[nVertex_NearField];
1655  su2double ZcoordRot = Xcoord[nVertex_NearField]*sin(AoA) + Zcoord[nVertex_NearField]*cos(AoA);
1656 
1657  /*--- Compute the Azimuthal angle ---*/
1658 
1659  su2double AngleDouble = fabs(atan(-YcoordRot/ZcoordRot)*180.0/PI_NUMBER);
1660 
1661  /*--- Fix an azimuthal line due to misalignments of the near-field ---*/
1662 
1663  su2double FixAzimuthalLine = config->GetFixAzimuthalLine();
1664 
1665  if ((AngleDouble >= FixAzimuthalLine - 0.1) && (AngleDouble <= FixAzimuthalLine + 0.1))
1666  AngleDouble = FixAzimuthalLine - 0.1;
1667 
1668  const auto AngleInt = SU2_TYPE::Short(floor(AngleDouble + 0.5));
1669 
1670  if (AngleInt >= 0) AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = AngleInt;
1671  else AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = 180 + AngleInt;
1672  }
1673 
1674  if (AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] <= 60) {
1675  IdPoint[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_IdPoint[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
1676  Pressure[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Pressure[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
1677  FaceArea[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_FaceArea[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
1678  IdDomain[nVertex_NearField] = iProcessor;
1679  nVertex_NearField++;
1680  }
1681  }
1682  }
1683 
1684 
1685  vector<short> PhiAngleList;
1686  vector<short>::iterator IterPhiAngleList;
1687 
1688  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex_NearField; iVertex++)
1689  PhiAngleList.push_back(AzimuthalAngle[iVertex]);
1690 
1691  sort( PhiAngleList.begin(), PhiAngleList.end());
1692  IterPhiAngleList = unique( PhiAngleList.begin(), PhiAngleList.end());
1693  PhiAngleList.resize( IterPhiAngleList - PhiAngleList.begin() );
1694 
1695  /*--- Create vectors and distribute the values among the different PhiAngle queues ---*/
1696 
1697  vector<vector<su2double> > Xcoord_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1698  vector<vector<su2double> > Ycoord_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1699  vector<vector<su2double> > Zcoord_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1700  vector<vector<unsigned long> > IdPoint_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1701  vector<vector<unsigned long> > IdDomain_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1702  vector<vector<su2double> > Pressure_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1703  vector<vector<su2double> > FaceArea_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1704  vector<vector<su2double> > EquivArea_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1705  vector<vector<su2double> > TargetArea_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1706  vector<vector<su2double> > NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1707  vector<vector<su2double> > Weight_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
1708 
1709  /*--- Distribute the values among the different PhiAngles ---*/
1710 
1711  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex_NearField; iVertex++)
1712  for (unsigned short iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
1713  if (AzimuthalAngle[iVertex] == PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle]) {
1714  Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Xcoord[iVertex]);
1715  Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Ycoord[iVertex]);
1716  Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Zcoord[iVertex]);
1717  IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(IdPoint[iVertex]);
1718  IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(IdDomain[iVertex]);
1719  Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Pressure[iVertex]);
1720  FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(FaceArea[iVertex]);
1721  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(EquivArea[iVertex]);
1722  TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(TargetArea[iVertex]);
1723  NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(NearFieldWeight[iVertex]);
1724  Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Weight[iVertex]);
1725  }
1726 
1727  /*--- Order the arrays (x Coordinate, Pressure, Point, and Domain) ---*/
1728 
1729  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
1730  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++)
1731  for (unsigned long jVertex = 0; jVertex < Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size() - 1 - iVertex; jVertex++)
1732  if (Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] > Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]) {
1733  auxXCoord = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxXCoord;
1734  auxYCoord = Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxYCoord;
1735  auxZCoord = Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxZCoord;
1736  auxPress = Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxPress;
1737  auxArea = FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxArea;
1738  auxPoint = IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxPoint;
1739  auxDomain = IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxDomain;
1740  }
1741 
1742 
1743  /*--- Check that all the azimuth lists have the same size ---*/
1744 
1745  auto nVertex = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0].size();
1746  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
1747  auto nVertex_aux = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size();
1748  if (nVertex_aux != nVertex) cout <<"Be careful! One azimuth list is shorter than the other.\n";
1749  nVertex = min(nVertex, nVertex_aux);
1750  }
1751 
1752  /*--- Compute equivalent area distribution at each azimuth angle ---*/
1753 
1754  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
1755  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][0] = 0.0;
1756  for (unsigned long iVertex = 1; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
1757  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 0.0;
1758 
1759  Coord_i = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*sin(AoA);
1760 
1761  for (unsigned long jVertex = 0; jVertex < iVertex-1; jVertex++) {
1762 
1763  Coord_j = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]*sin(AoA);
1764  jp1Coord = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]*sin(AoA);
1765 
1766  jFunction = factor*(Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] - Pressure_Inf)*sqrt(Coord_i-Coord_j);
1767  jp1Function = factor*(Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] - Pressure_Inf)*sqrt(Coord_i-jp1Coord);
1768 
1769  DeltaX = (jp1Coord-Coord_j);
1770  MeanFunction = 0.5*(jp1Function + jFunction);
1771  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] += DeltaX * MeanFunction;
1772  }
1773  }
1774  }
1775 
1776  /*--- Create a file with the equivalent area distribution at each azimuthal angle ---*/
1777 
1778  NearFieldEA_file.precision(config->GetOutput_Precision());
1779 
1780  NearFieldEA_file.open("Equivalent_Area.dat", ios::out);
1781  NearFieldEA_file << "TITLE = \"Equivalent Area evaluation at each azimuthal angle\"" << "\n";
1782 
1783  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
1784  NearFieldEA_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (in) at r="<< R_Plane*12.0 << " in. (cyl. coord. system)\"";
1785  else
1786  NearFieldEA_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (m) at r="<< R_Plane << " m. (cylindrical coordinate system)\"";
1787 
1788  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
1789  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
1790  NearFieldEA_file << ", \"Equivalent Area (ft<sup>2</sup>), <greek>F</greek>= " << PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle] << " deg.\"";
1791  else
1792  NearFieldEA_file << ", \"Equivalent Area (m<sup>2</sup>), <greek>F</greek>= " << PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle] << " deg.\"";
1793  }
1794 
1795  NearFieldEA_file << "\n";
1796  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[0].size(); iVertex++) {
1797 
1798  su2double XcoordRot = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*sin(AoA);
1799  su2double XcoordRot_init = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*sin(AoA);
1800 
1801  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
1802  NearFieldEA_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init) * 12.0;
1803  else
1804  NearFieldEA_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init);
1805 
1806  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
1807  NearFieldEA_file << scientific << ", " << EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
1808  }
1809 
1810  NearFieldEA_file << "\n";
1811 
1812  }
1813  NearFieldEA_file.close();
1814 
1815 
1816  /*--- Read target equivalent area from the configuration file,
1817  this first implementation requires a complete table (same as the original
1818  EA table). so... no interpolation. ---*/
1819 
1820  vector<vector<su2double> > TargetArea_PhiAngle_Trans;
1821  TargetEA_file.open("TargetEA.dat", ios::in);
1822 
1823  if (TargetEA_file.fail()) {
1824  /*--- Set the table to 0 ---*/
1825  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
1826  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++)
1827  TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 0.0;
1828  }
1829  else {
1830 
1831  /*--- skip header lines ---*/
1832 
1833  string line;
1834  getline(TargetEA_file, line);
1835  getline(TargetEA_file, line);
1836 
1837  while (TargetEA_file) {
1838 
1839  string line;
1840  getline(TargetEA_file, line);
1841  istringstream is(line);
1842  vector<su2double> row;
1843  unsigned short iter = 0;
1844 
1845  while (is.good()) {
1846  string token;
1847  getline(is, token,',');
1848 
1849  istringstream js(token);
1850 
1851  su2double data;
1852  js >> data;
1853 
1854  /*--- The first element in the table is the coordinate (in or m)---*/
1855 
1856  if (iter != 0) row.push_back(data);
1857  iter++;
1858 
1859  }
1860  TargetArea_PhiAngle_Trans.push_back(row);
1861  }
1862 
1863  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
1864  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++)
1865  TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = TargetArea_PhiAngle_Trans[iVertex][iPhiAngle];
1866 
1867  }
1868 
1869  /*--- Divide by the number of Phi angles in the nearfield ---*/
1870 
1871  su2double PhiFactor = 1.0/su2double(PhiAngleList.size());
1872 
1873  /*--- Evaluate the objective function ---*/
1874 
1875  InverseDesign = 0;
1876  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
1877  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
1878  Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 1.0;
1879  Coord_i = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
1880 
1881  su2double Difference = EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]-TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
1882  su2double percentage = fabs(Difference)*100/fabs(TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]);
1883 
1884  if ((percentage < 0.1) || (Coord_i < XCoordBegin_OF) || (Coord_i > XCoordEnd_OF)) Difference = 0.0;
1885 
1886  InverseDesign += EAScaleFactor*PhiFactor*Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*Difference*Difference;
1887  }
1888 
1889  /*--- Evaluate the weight of the nearfield pressure (adjoint input) ---*/
1890 
1891  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
1892  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
1893  Coord_i = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
1894  NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 0.0;
1895  for (unsigned long jVertex = iVertex; jVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); jVertex++) {
1896  Coord_j = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex];
1897  Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 1.0;
1898 
1899  su2double Difference = EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]-TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex];
1900  su2double percentage = fabs(Difference)*100/fabs(TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]);
1901 
1902  if ((percentage < 0.1) || (Coord_j < XCoordBegin_OF) || (Coord_j > XCoordEnd_OF)) Difference = 0.0;
1903 
1904  NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] += EAScaleFactor*PhiFactor*Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*2.0*Difference*factor*sqrt(Coord_j-Coord_i);
1905  }
1906  }
1907  }
1908 
1909  /*--- Write the Nearfield pressure at each Azimuthal PhiAngle ---*/
1910 
1911  EquivArea_file.precision(config->GetOutput_Precision());
1912 
1913  EquivArea_file.open("nearfield_flow.dat", ios::out);
1914  EquivArea_file << "TITLE = \"Equivalent Area evaluation at each azimuthal angle\"" << "\n";
1915 
1916  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
1917  EquivArea_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (in) at r="<< R_Plane*12.0 << " in. (cyl. coord. system)\",\"Equivalent Area (ft<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Target Equivalent Area (ft<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Cp\"" << "\n";
1918  else
1919  EquivArea_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (m) at r="<< R_Plane << " m. (cylindrical coordinate system)\",\"Equivalent Area (m<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Target Equivalent Area (m<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Cp\"" << "\n";
1920 
1921  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
1922  EquivArea_file << fixed << "ZONE T= \"<greek>F</greek>=" << PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle] << " deg.\"" << "\n";
1923  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
1924 
1925  su2double XcoordRot = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*sin(AoA);
1926  su2double XcoordRot_init = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*sin(AoA);
1927 
1928  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
1929  EquivArea_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init) * 12.0;
1930  else
1931  EquivArea_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init);
1932 
1933  EquivArea_file << scientific << ", " << EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]
1934  << ", " << TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] << ", " << (Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]-Pressure_Inf)/Pressure_Inf << "\n";
1935  }
1936  }
1937 
1938  EquivArea_file.close();
1939 
1940  }
1941 
1942  /*--- Send the value of the NearField coefficient to all the processors ---*/
1943 
1944  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&InverseDesign, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1945 
1946  /*--- Store the value of the NearField coefficient ---*/
1947 
1948  solver->SetTotal_CEquivArea(InverseDesign);
1949  SetHistoryOutputValue("EQUIVALENT_AREA", InverseDesign);
1950 
1951 }

3511 bool CFlowOutput::WriteVolume_Output(CConfig *config, unsigned long Iter, bool force_writing, unsigned short iFile){
3512 
3513  bool writeRestart = false;
3514  auto FileFormat = config->GetVolumeOutputFiles();
3515 
3516  if (config->GetTime_Domain()){
3517  if (((config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST) || (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::TIME_STEPPING)) &&
3518  ((Iter == 0) || (Iter % config->GetVolumeOutputFrequency(iFile) == 0))){
3519  return true;
3520  }
3521 
3522  /* check if we want to write a restart file*/
3523  if (FileFormat[iFile] == OUTPUT_TYPE::RESTART_ASCII || FileFormat[iFile] == OUTPUT_TYPE::RESTART_BINARY || FileFormat[iFile] == OUTPUT_TYPE::CSV) {
3524  writeRestart = true;
3525  }
3526 
3527  /* only write 'double' files for the restart files */
3528  if ((config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_2ND) &&
3529  ((Iter == 0) || (Iter % config->GetVolumeOutputFrequency(iFile) == 0) ||
3530  (((Iter+1) % config->GetVolumeOutputFrequency(iFile) == 0) && writeRestart==true) || // Restarts need 2 old solutions.
3531  (((Iter+2) == config->GetnTime_Iter()) && writeRestart==true))){ // The last timestep is written anyway but one needs the step before for restarts.
3532  return true;
3533  }
3534  } else {
3535  if (config->GetFixed_CL_Mode() && config->GetFinite_Difference_Mode()) return false;
3536  return ((Iter > 0) && Iter % config->GetVolumeOutputFrequency(iFile) == 0) || force_writing;
3537  }
3538 
3539  return false || force_writing;
3540 }

3568 void CFlowOutput::LoadTimeAveragedData(unsigned long iPoint, const CVariable *Node_Flow){
3569  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_DENSITY", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetDensity(iPoint));
3570  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-X", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,0));
3571  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-Y", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,1));
3572  if (nDim == 3)
3573  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-Z", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,2));
3574 
3575  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_PRESSURE", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetPressure(iPoint));
3576 
3577  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_U", iPoint, pow(Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,0),2));
3578  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_V", iPoint, pow(Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,1),2));
3579  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_UV", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,0) * Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,1));
3580  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_P", iPoint, pow(Node_Flow->GetPressure(iPoint),2));
3581  if (nDim == 3){
3582  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_W", iPoint, pow(Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,2),2));
3583  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_VW", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,2) * Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,1));
3584  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_UW", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,2) * Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,0));
3585  }
3586 
3587  const su2double umean = GetVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-X", iPoint);
3588  const su2double uumean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_U", iPoint);
3589  const su2double vmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-Y", iPoint);
3590  const su2double vvmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_V", iPoint);
3591  const su2double uvmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_UV", iPoint);
3592  const su2double pmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_PRESSURE", iPoint);
3593  const su2double ppmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_P", iPoint);
3594 
3595  SetVolumeOutputValue("UUPRIME", iPoint, -(umean*umean - uumean));
3596  SetVolumeOutputValue("VVPRIME", iPoint, -(vmean*vmean - vvmean));
3597  SetVolumeOutputValue("UVPRIME", iPoint, -(umean*vmean - uvmean));
3598  SetVolumeOutputValue("PPRIME", iPoint, -(pmean*pmean - ppmean));
3599  if (nDim == 3){
3600  const su2double wmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-Z", iPoint);
3601  const su2double wwmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_W", iPoint);
3602  const su2double uwmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_UW", iPoint);
3603  const su2double vwmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_VW", iPoint);
3604  SetVolumeOutputValue("WWPRIME", iPoint, -(wmean*wmean - wwmean));
3605  SetVolumeOutputValue("UWPRIME", iPoint, -(umean*wmean - uwmean));
3606  SetVolumeOutputValue("VWPRIME", iPoint, -(vmean*wmean - vwmean));
3607  }
3608 }
